# 🧠 Day 21 – Weekly Review & Quiz (DevOps Fundamentals)

This repository contains notes, quiz responses, and key revision areas from **Day 21** of the [30-Day DevOps Mastery Plan](#).  
The purpose of Day 21 is to **review the past 3 weeks** of learning and test our understanding across core DevOps areas.

---

## 📋 Topics Covered

| Topic       | Skills Reviewed |
|-------------|------------------|
| ✅ Linux     | Commands, permissions, file system |
| ✅ Docker    | Images, containers, volumes, networking |
| ✅ Jenkins   | Jobs, pipelines, CI/CD automation |
| ✅ Terraform | Resources, providers, state files |
| ✅ Kubernetes| Pods, Services, Deployments, ConfigMaps, Secrets |

